267
00:18:18,310 --> 00:18:20,710
Cheng Lang accompanied me to the clinic.

268
00:18:20,710 --> 00:18:22,010
How do you feel now?

269
00:18:22,010 --> 00:18:23,180
Are you all right?

270
00:18:23,180 --> 00:18:25,760
