290
00:19:44,140 --> 00:19:45,340
<i>[Third Class Carriage]</i>

291
00:19:46,980 --> 00:19:49,780
<i>[Yunhai Station]</i>

292
00:19:49,780 --> 00:19:51,340
<i>[Exit]</i>

